harge to the endpoint of the trailing string in $AdS_5$\nrepresenting a heavy quark. This leads to modified Nambu-Goto equations for the\nstring which govern the (collisional and radiative) energy loss by the heavy\nquark towards both hard and soft modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Oct 2014 18:41:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Dec 2014 14:30:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2015 16:11:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-10"}
