lerating phase followed by a\nmatter dominated phase of the universe. The permitted range of values of the\nEoS parameters and the associated parameters ($f$, $\\gamma$, $\\omega$,\n$\\Omega$, $c^2_{s}$, $q$) are compared with those obtained earlier using other\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Oct 2014 06:18:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2015 11:40:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-02"}
